title: How To Replace Or Swap Door Lock Handles To Change Locks Or Keys Quick
tags: ['Kung', 'Fu', 'Maintenance', 'Demonstrates', 'Shows', 'How', 'To', 'Replace', 'Or', 'Swap', 'Door', 'Lock', 'Handles', 'Change', 'Locks', 'Keys', 'Quick', 'Fast', 'Easy', 'Rekey', 'Set', 'Simple', 'Thumb', 'Latch', 'Lock Sticking', 'Most Often', 'Cause', 'Screws', 'Too', 'Tight', 'Fix', 'Loosen', 'Set Screws', 'Hand', 'Latch Plate', 'How-to', 'Repair', 'Turn', 'Stick', 'Press', 'Close', 'Open', 'Old', 'New', 'Check', 'Proper', 'Operation', 'Good', 'To Go', 'Tutorial', 'Tips', 'How To Change Locks', 'How To Swap', 'Swap Handles', 'Change Door Locks', 'Replace Door Locks', 'DIY', 'Save', 'Do It Yourself', 'How To', 'Help', 'Next']
description:
Kung Fu Maintenance shows how easy you can swap, replace, or change door lock handles to change locks or keys quick. Buy The Kung Fu Maintenance E Book Here
http://www.amazon.com/Kung-Fu-Maintenance-ebook/dp/B007KQFI3Q/ref=sr_1_1_bnp_1_kin?ie=UTF8&qid=1379045417&sr=8-1&keywords=Kung+Fu+Maintenance

http://KungFuMaintenance.Com
http://Blog.KungFuMaintenance.Com
http://Arcade.KungFuMaintenance.Com http://VGBlog.KungFuMaintenance.Com
http://TheMaintenanceEar.KungFuMaintenance.Com

Today I am going to show you how easy it is to change these locks. These have kind of a quick nice and easy feature in how they slip together. So let me show you here. You can see the slots in the back of this here. What you do is line up your post hole. You can turn it so that it slides in and than this slips into place. Than you are able to tighten the screws through here. So it is just a quick deal to get it going. So here it is on the door itself. Taking off the old lock. All we have to do is loosen up the screws on both sides. Than rotate it and pull the old one out.  On the new one we will just pass it through our holes. Like so and rotate in the new deal. Tighten the screws down on both sides. And we are all set there. Ready to go. Now one of the most common causes of sticking locks is if your screws are too tight. So if you see your post is sticking that would be one of the first things to check. Either these two screws or these two screws may be too tight so. Make sure our deal closes properly and we are all set there. Good to go.

description:
Let's play Five Nights at Freddy's. In this episode we complete Day 2 - and there's a bonus scare!

Welcome to your new summer job at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. The animatronic robots' behavior has become somewhat unpredictable at night, and it was much cheaper to hire you as a security guard than to find a repairman. 

From your small office you must watch the security cameras carefully. You have a very limited amount of electricity that you're allowed to use per night (corporate budget cuts, you know). title: Как медитация воздействует на мозг
description:
Это видео представляет собой трехмерную энцефаллограмму головного мозга, снятую во время прослушивания медитации, разработаной в Институте совершенствования сознания. Теперь вы можете увидеть своими глазами как мозг реагирует на медитативные программы, как возникают нейронные импульсы, как мозг реагирует на акустическое воздействие. Эта программа не медитация (в ней представлен фрагмент медитативной программы), она предназначена для визуализации процессов, происходящих в мозгу во время работы с нейроакустическими программами, разрабатываемыми в Институте совершенствования сознания.  Дело в том, что в наших программах используются частоты, которые невозможно услышать человеческим ухом, а вот мозг их прекрасно слышит и реагирует. Теперь у вас появилась возможность "заглянуть" в мозг и увидеть своими глазами как именно работает нейроакустическая программа, увидеть явление биорезонанса (в программе звучит фрагмент медитации "Биорезонанс частот вознесения").

title: (NEW)City Escape Low Score 0
description:
This video is better than the last one, has 2 minutes less, a better landing and a better view
I changed the strategy a little and may I'll delete the previous video

City Escape was an impossible level to be finished with 0 points

Cause, when you come to the area of the last checkpoint you get some points, and when you go to the truck part you get some rings and more points

Thanks Jawzun for finding this awesome glitch that I used at 1:48
It's the only way to avoid the last checkpoint area and begining of the truck part

About the glitch, I think it's one of the most or the most hard to be done in sa2
It's very hard to pass through the "invisible wall" with enough speed to "fly", when you pass through it with unless necessary speed sonic will "fly" a bit and then will fall

And, you need to wait till 9:20 to finish the level, If you pass through the goal ring before 9:20 you will get points

I did it playing on GameCube, the gravity glitch may work on Dreamcast, but didn't worked to me, maybe because I tried only a little

I Increased the speed of some parts of the video, like the failed attemps to perform the glitch and the time you have to wait at the end

About the box skiping at 0:44, I found it by myself

title: The Chef and The Dietitian #54 - Overnight Muesli
description:
MUESLI
1/2 cup gluten-free oats
2 Tablespoons currants
1 Tablespoon chia seeds
1/2 teaspoon apple pie spice
2 ounces apple juice
2 ounces unsweetened almond milk
1 teaspoon alcohol-free vanilla (optional)
fresh apple

Place gluten-free oats, currants, chia seeds and apple pie spice into a mixing bowl. Add apple juice and unsweetened almond milk. Add alcohol-free vanilla (optional) if using. Grate fresh apple over the top of the bowl. Mix. Place in refrigerator overnight.

title: Duck eggs can easily be hatched by using broody chicken hens
tags: ['Bird', 'Pinaki', 'Brooding', 'Birds', 'Chicken (Organism Classification)', 'Ducks', 'Duck', 'Wildlife', 'Nature', 'Poultry (CSA Product)', 'Nest', 'Loving (TV Program)', 'Love (Quotation Addressee)', 'Caring Is Creepy (Composition)', 'Broodiness', 'CARE (Organization)', 'Loving You (Film)', 'Mother Teresa (Saint)', "Mother's Day (Holiday)", 'Mother (Relation)', 'Animals']
description:
For more details video on brooding of chickens using a duck check this https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g83VuESp0qE 
Do you know the hens can brood the duck eggs for you.  You can leave them with their mother because a mother always takes care of their child because mother is always a mother. More and more individuals are choosing to hatch duck eggs, in choice or in place of chicken eggs. There are a few different ways to hatch ducklings, but using a chicken is perhaps the simplest method. Duck eggs can easily be hatched by using broody chicken hens. I put some fertile eggs under her (the hen). She incubated them very well and as soon as they hatched she started taking care of the ducklings as her own child & use to feed them regularly as you can see them in this video. For the small poultry keeper there is the choice of two methods of hatching chicks - natural or artificial. The best idea is to gain experience and confidence in both. Hen eggs take 21 days to hatch, duck and turkey eggs 28 days, most goose eggs 28 - 30 days and Muscovy eggs 35 days. Some very small bantam eggs may be a day early and really large poultry such as Cochins may be a day extra.

title: En 3 minutes, la construction d'une cabane en bois
description: En moins de 3 minutes, visionner en accéléré la construction d'une cabane de jardin faite en bois brut acheté directement en scierie. Les outils utilisés : brouette, niveau, truelle, perceuse, scie à onglet, scie égoïne, rabot, visseuse, marteau, brosse à peinture, compresseur, échelle, escabeau. Comment est fabriqué cet abris de jardin : d'une base en agglos (parpaings de 10 cm) assemblés avec du béton et posés à niveau, de bois autoclave pour l'ossature, des planches sapin de 20 mm traitées et utilisées pour le plancher, les parois extérieures, le plafond, et pour soutenir les plaques ondulées PVC qui sert d'étanchéité et de toiture. En finition, j'ai appliqué sur le bois extérieur 2 couches d'une peinture azure et pour l'intérieur, j'ai posé du lambris blanc et du parquet flottant (comme dans les chambres de la maison). La cabane ne possède pas de fenêtre, car la toiture en plaques ongulées PVC transparentes laisse passer la lumière du soleil, et même un peu trop.

최강희 감독이 지휘하는 전북은 26일 중국 베이징에 위치한 베이징공인체육장에서 열린 AFC 챔피언스리그 16강 2차전 베이징 궈안(중국)과 원정경기에서 1-0으로 승리를 거뒀다. 후반 27분 에두가 선제골을 넣은 전북은 끝까지 리드를 지켜내며 승리를 차지했다. 1·2차전 합계 2-1로 앞선 전북은 8강행 티켓을 거머쥐었다. 전북의 AFC 챔피언스리그 8강행은 2011년 이후 4년 만이다.

title: A Quick view of some of our flying during our Campaign for SVEEP 2013!
description:
If you thought general aviation (more specifically, sport aviation) in India is pretty much dead, you're only partly right.

For the second time, the State Election Commission has employed the services of Meghalaya Paragliding Association to fly low and slow over various cities and towns, flying a banner and dropping pamphlets from the air. The banner and pamphlets carried a message: urging everyone to exercise their right to vote.

Here is a short video that shows you some of the sights and places we enjoyed during our month long campaign at Karnataka. We flew a paramotor trike manufactured by Albatross Flying Systems, Bangalore, and flown by a very skilled pilot: Nikolai Singh, from Meghalaya Paragliding Association. 

We flew not just ourselves, but the Deputy Commissioners of various districts, such as Karwar, Belgaum, Koppal, Tumkur, Davangere. We also flew the SP of Police, Tumkur. All flights were with the coordination and support of the local police, government, Air Force, and Air Traffic Control.

Enjoy the 2 minute video!

Thanks to good music from the Celestial Aeon_Project "Lords of the Sky"!

title: 8Dio Agitato Grandiose Legato Cellos
description:
This video demonstrates 8Dio Agitato Grandiose Legato Ensemble and Divisi Cellos. A comprehensive music software (VST) instrument that allows you to play completely realistic symphonic cellos.

Agitato Grandiose Legato is inspired by the soaring melodic styles of Williams and Mancini and designed as fast melodic leads for any string library of your choice.

Agitato Grandiose Legato For Cellos consists of 7 different types of legato, starting with our new beautiful and smooth sustain x-fade. We also included more gentle legatos (ex. gentle and gentle detache), however if you are looking for a traditional soaring Hollywood inspired sound – we recommend our two Mancini Legatos, which brings forward that gorgeous, intense molto vibrato.

Agitato Grandiose Legato contains a completely new legato system, which is more flexible then ever. You have full control over dynamics and expression, including the ability to link the two. In addition we have a new highly adaptive legato speed system, which really allows the legato to adapt to your compositional style and preference.

More information at www.8dio.com

title: [MMV] Airplanes.
description:
Edit; 07.20.11,
Wow guys; becus of you this video has 14k views! (: I can't thank you ENOUGH for getting me so many. I LOVE YOU ALL :D FREE UNLICKED COOKIES FOR EVERYONE!

WOW. MY FIRST FULL MMV LMFAO IM SO PROUD OF MYSELF. F2.

- First things first, I want to give the BIGGEST FUCKIN` SHOUTOUT EVER, to starryangel101 for literaly making me finish this (: I LOVE YOU CRYSTAL LOL. 
     Seriously, go subscribe her. She's so pro nd` shes the best motherfckin` friend. (: 

- Secondly! Another shoutout to one of my friends who doesnt have a yt, shes the one who nags at me and goes "EMMA YOU DONT HAVE A FREAKING FULL MMV, GO MAKE ONE!" While I sulk in the corner and cry. ): 

- Thirdly! Songs called Airplanes by Travis Garland.
 
- Fourthy! This started on June 07, 2010. And ended September 13, 2010. Im not sure whether to be proud or annoyed. LOL

- Fifthy! 
In no way do I claim copyrights of this song, or the pictures used. All credits go towards Travis Garland for the song, Nexon Inc. for the sprites, and Sony Vegas as my editing program. All rights reserved!

STORYLINE TIME LOL. (long, be warned!)
---------------------------------------------------------
Note; Since the song IS called Airplanes, I decided to make a special meaning for it. :) Read in the *s.

When the guy was in elementaryish, hes basically a guy with huge glasses in his school. But then this girl transfers into his school & he falls in love, but the boy gets picked on for doing so. The girl saw him staring at her and wondered if he liked her, like she liked him. So, since this was still on her first day at school, She started hanging out with him, teaching him about life , love , and whatnot. Whenever the girl saw the boy getting picked, she would run over to him and say things to the bullies to make em' run like hell. (Girl power ftw?).
Once the girl and boy grad. from their elementary/secondary school, The girl and guy have changed drastically. The girl has more friends now, popular & 'hot'. And the guy is a jock, popular but part of a different clique, smart & still loves the girl, but he believes she changed too much and doesn't like him anymore. (They rarely hang out / see each other unless its a friendly nod in the hallways.) The guy starts becoming an insomiac, (His subconcious keeps reminding him about her everyday) and he starts to feel her next to him like it was before (hallucinations) but, in reality, she isn't. Even though he think she moved on & never liked him (She does!) he keeps believing that if he said 'I Love You' to the girl, things would have been different & they would still be together. (he was her everything) *Now & then, in the night the boy would go out to where he had first kissed her & stare out at the sky. Airplanes always flew by, so he compaired the airplanes to shooting stars & said to himself "I could really use a wish right now..."*
Then he falls asleep on the hill and dreams that hes running to try to catch up to the girl (shes going up stairs) and at the top, there's a giant door, (Heavens door), so once the girl gets there, the boy gives up and hopes that she doesn't look down.
When the boy wakes up and starts walking home, he thinks about writing a song to the girl, so that she would notice him & see his true feelings for her. 
At the end, once he's finished his song, he starts to think of the worst cast scenarios. (she'll laugh at him and call him a weirdo, show it to her friends, reject him cruelly, etc.) So, the boy rips the song up and goes back to the place where they first kissed, but he brings a knife with him because he thinks no one cares about him & he wants to end his life.
When he goes back to this place, he's about to stab himself when another plane flies over again, & he thinks it's a sign to not kill himself, so he gets out of his odd depressionative state & starts to cry, but then falls over & faints from lack of food nd sleep.
When he dreams, he dreams of her going up the stairs once more, but this time, he catches up to her and tries to tell her i love you, but then hes woken up by the girl whos really worried about him. When he wakes up, he THEN smiles at her and says I Love You, as he passes out right in front of her.
2 Months Later, the girl is graduating from HS but as she goes to get her diploma, she sees him standing infront of her teachers and she runs over to him and hugs him, while he gives her a kiss.
And if you actually read this entire wall of text, I love you more. LOL

description:
AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA

Es una agrupación del genero Tropical, compuesta por 10 músicos de gran trayectoria y reconocimiento en el medio musical

La agrupación musical AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA, es un producto exclusivo de CANTO AZUL PRODUCCIONES, empresa reconocida en la promoción de grandes artistas y espectáculos

Artistas que han desfilado por grandes escenarios dentro y fuera de la ciudad, que en su momento decidieron conformar esta fantástica agrupación 

"AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA", funciona bajo la dirección de su director Robinson Arenas, músico de gran trayectoria, profesor de música, cantante, arreglista y compositor, con el único objetivo de crear una agrupación de altísima calidad que compitiera con grandes Orquestas en todo América Latina. 

Una agrupación que reúne toda la belleza, el sabor, y la tradición de la música tropical de todos los tiempos, al estilo de las grandes orquestas del mundo conservando las versiones originales de aquellas canciones que han sido el deleite de las fiestas en todas las épocas.

AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA, es una agrupación versátil para todo tipo de eventos familiares o empresariales en los que prime el gusto por los ritmos tropicales, y en especial para grandes escenarios y tarimas municipales.

AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA se especializa en ritmos tropicales de todas las regiones de Colombia, como lo es el porro, la cumbia, y todos los aires sabaneros mas sonados en todo el pais.

AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA, se adapta a cualquier escenario dentro y fuera de la ciudad y del país.

En sus interpretaciones podemos destacar las versiones originales de artistas como Los hispanos, los graduados, Rodolfo Aicardi, los corraleros, etc, siempre conservando sus versiones originales.

RIDER TÉCNICO DE LA AGRUPACIÓN AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA
La agrupación musical AZUL TROPICAL ORQUESTA, solo se presenta con amplificación de audio adecuada al espacio, y al tamaño del escenario, o lugar del evento.
Sus requerimientos técnicos son:
• Consola de audio de 16 a 24 canales con monitores al frente
• líneas para instrumento
• Micrófonos para voces con su respectivas bases articuladas

Visit http://www.cincinnatiavionics.com for more information or to get a quote!

Sporty's Cincinnati Avionics is pleased to announce the availability of Garmin's new GTN series.  

Garmin's new touch-screen, panel-mount navigators - or GTN series - is the latest in the series of GPS NAV COMM products that have revolutionized the way pilots fly.  Combining the latest in MFD features with touch screen controls for data entry and radio tuning, the GTN series offers amazing, but simple-to-use technology that will once again bring a new level of sophistication and situational awareness to the flight deck.

A new graphical interface with icons as touch keys makes functions and menu options easy to locate on the units' large, high-resolution TFT displays.

title: New Marc MP36 Engine 15
tags: ['Marc', '15', 'mp-36', 'diesel', 'engine', 'green', 'power', 'ulsd', 'ultra', 'low', 'sulfer', 'fuel', 'environmentally', 'freindly', 'safe', 'clean', 'emissions', 'efficient', 'economical', 'marc', 'maryland', 'rail', 'commuter', 'yard', 'locust', 'baltimore', 'i-95', 'riverside', 'csx', 'fueling', 'railfan', 'Train', 'Railroad', 'Trains', 'Change', 'Warming', 'Global', 'Energy', 'Keretapi Tanah Melayu (Mass Transportation System)', 'Federal Hill (Neighborhood)', 'Climate', 'Solar', 'Solar Energy (Industry)', 'MPI MPXpress', 'MARC Train (Mass Transportation System)', 'special rare ervans', 'csxt', 'transport']
description:
sorry, had to use long zoom...

  "MPXpress is a series of diesel-electric passenger train locomotives designed for commuter rail service. The manufacturer, Motive Power, offers the locomotives with a number of customizable options such as different prime movers and traction motors, head end power (HEP) generated by a separate engine or by the prime mover, and new or refurbished trucks. To date, MPI has offered three main variants: MP36PH-3S, MP36PH-3C, and MP40PH-3C.

The MPXpress line of locomotives were the first production passenger locomotives to meet EPA Tier 1 emissions regulations, as well as FRA safety regulations regarding crash-worthiness and fire safety. The line also meets APTA crash-worthiness standards.

Numerous public transit agencies in Canada and the United States have ordered MPXpress locomotives for their commuter rail services.

 
The MP36PH-3S uses a 16-cylinder MPI 645F3B diesel engine as its prime mover. Its HEP is generated from a static inverter that receives its power through connections to the prime mover. When providing full electrical power to the passenger cars connected to it, the prime mover must maintain a higher RPM in order to supply power to the passenger cars. The traction power when providing full HEP load of 500Kw is 2930 HP, since HEP generation diverts some power from the prime mover.

Chicago's Metra has ordered 27 of these locomotives, which were built and delivered from 2003 through 2004. 14 were to replace Metra's aged F40C fleet; the rest were for expansion. When the locomotives were first delivered, they exhibited software and computer problems, to the point that Metra had to put two F40Cs back into service for a short time in 2004. One of the unique features of the MP36s in Metra's fleet compared to other operators is that they are equipped with a Gyralite (which is standard equipment on all of Metra's passenger locomotives), which are mounted in the spot where the train number board would be located on the front of the locomotive.

[edit] MP36PH-3C
The MP36PH-3C has the same prime mover as the "-3S" model, the MPI 645F3B diesel engine, but with its HEP generated by a separate Caterpillar diesel engine, thus the "C" in its model name. In this arrangement, when providing HEP, the full 3600 HP from the prime mover is available for traction, and the prime mover is allowed to idle at a lower RPM. Caltrain was the first to purchase the MP36PH-3C in 2003.

The MP36PH-3C is currently the top-selling commuter locomotive in North America.

[edit] MP40PH-3C
The MP40PH-3C is similar to the MP36PH-3C, but with several differences:

the MP40PH-3C uses a 16-cylinder EMD 710GB series diesel engine instead of the MPI 645F3B, generating 4000HP instead of 3600. 
the use of EMD's EM2000 computer and associated control system instead of Wabtec/MPI's own system in the MP36. 
the use of an EMD alternator and traction motors. 
GO Transit ordered 27 locomotives of this model, which were delivered throughout 2008. An order for 20 additional units was signed in July 2008.

description:
http://www.expobuilding.net/video.aspx


Si posiziona un profilo separatore tra interno doccia e il resto del bagno
Le piastrelle del rivestimento vengono incollate con Keraflex Maxi S1 adatto a pareti irregolari o con dislivelli con cui si realizzano spessori fino a 1,5 cm
L’adesivo si applica con spatola metallica Raimondi, a dente quadrato, del 10.                                          
Quindi si inizia a posare il rivestimento del box in mosaico
Si utilizza il frattazzo in gomma Mapei per il posizionamento e la registrazione dei fogli in mosaico 
Terminato il rivestimento della prima parete, si procede con la seconda parete
Il collante utilizzato è sempre il Keraflex Maxi S1
Si ripete nuovamente il procedimento visto in precedenza.

Destiny is set seven hundred years into the future in a post-apocalyptic setting following a prosperous period of exploration, peace and technological advancement known as the Golden Age. In a universe where humans have spread out and colonized planets in the Solar System, an event known as "the Collapse" saw the mysterious dissolution of these colonies, the end of the Golden Age, and mankind teetering on the brink of extinction. The only known survivors of the Collapse are those living on Earth, who were saved by "the Traveller", a white, spherical celestial body whose appearance centuries before had enabled humans to reach the stars. The Traveller now hovers above the last remaining human city, and its presence allows the "Guardians of the City"—the last defenders of the human race—the ability to wield an unknown power, only referred to as "The Light".
Upon mankind's first attempt to repopulate and reconstruct after the Collapse, it is discovered that hostile alien races have occupied mankind's former colonies and civilizations and are now encroaching upon the City. The player takes on the role of a Guardian of the City, and is tasked with investigating and destroying these threats before humanity is completely wiped out.

Knowing... When to say When, Uncle!, or Enough is Enough

description:
ボートレース平和島 http://www.heiwajima.gr.jp/
ボートレースは6艇のボートが１周６００mの水面を左回りに３周するレースです。
右手でステアリング、左手でスロットル、４００ｃｃ2サイクル縦型直列2気筒、水面を80キロで走ります。スタートはフライングスタート方式でコンマ0.00秒を競います。
水面では年齢も性別も先輩・後輩もありません。その故、水上の格闘技と言われています。
レーサー達はただひとつ、「勝利」を目指して果敢にレースに挑みます。
そんなエキサイティングなボートレースの迫力をお伝えするべく、ボートにカメラを設置し撮影しました。
レーサーは「ドラゴン」と呼ばれる　山田　竜一選手。レースに対する飽くなき姿勢と豪快なターン通称「ドラゴンターン」でファンを魅了し続けているレーサーです。
ボートレース平和島は年間180日開催しています。スタンド水面際では目の前10m弱でレースがご覧になれます！ぜひ、一度ご来場下さい！

title: FSX: Impossible landing? default Boeing 747-400 at SABA in a thunderstorm HD 720
description:
A near perfect landing on one hell of a short runway! Preceded by a short helo flight around the landing strip just to show what I was up against.

I KNOW [or assume] that this would be impossible in real life, but even in MS FSX it's one hell of a challenge! I was hoping to be the 1st and I was gutted when I found out that several other have beaten me to it, so I decided to go one better & do it in a thunderstorm... I lost count of how many attempts were needed but my patience finally paid off.

I'm using the [excellent] FLYTAMPA scenery (in conjunction with REX) - the default FSX scenery has trees in the approach making it impossible with crash detection on.

Music: O Fortuna


Computer spec:

Original manufacturer: Packard Bell 

AMD Athlon64 x2 4000+ 2.1Ghz [tried overclocking but this caused stability issues]

3Gb DDR2.

512Mb XFX Nvidia GeForce 9600GT

120Gb Seagate SATA drive with a dual-boot configuration for Vista/XP

1TB Seagate SATA drive for demanding programs & media

*I run FSX under XP and installed it to the secondary HDD

title: 2012漢神奧斯卡之夜-小蝦模仿秀
Everybody Hurts (R.E.M.) Guitar/Vocal Cover
description:
Please "Show more"! :)

Hello! This is my first guitar/vocal cover out here on YouTube... I decided to differentiate this time, because I recently saw my subscribers raise to 100!! (Yeah, I know, it's not a big deal, but it kindly was for me!)

Please "stay tuned" until the end of the video for a special message. :-)

I decided to cover "Everybody Hurts", since it has always been one of my favorite songs to listen to. 

As you'll see, I played a couple of "strokes that sound bad"! :P Please be gentle with my guitar skills... I haven't had any guitar lessons so what I play is what I've learned by myself! But any kind of advice is welcome! :)

As for the vocal part, it starts out a bit "flat" but it does get a little better afterwards... Sorry for not being able to do the backing vocals as well but my recording equipment didn't help me a lot this time... I had to record audio with a camera, which wouldn't offer such a good quality...

But despite all that, I kinda like the result! What do you think? Please tell me your opinion! Comments are more than welcome and, if you liked this video, don't hesitate to give a "thumbs-up"!

Sincerely thank you all for your support so far,
Natalia

^_^

IMPORTANT NOTE: THIS IS A COVER SONG OF "EVERYBODY HURTS", ORIGINALLY COMPOSED BY R.E.M. IN 1993 AND RELEASED IN THE ALBUM "AUTOMATIC FOR THE PEOPLE". I DO NOT CLAIM ANY COPYRIGHT FOR ITS COMPOSITION.

description:
GIving Lady Sovereign's "I Got You Dancing" a shot on hard mode in Dance Central. It's a really fun routine with plenty of static moves between higher impact dancing to help you catch your breath. title: RUMBO A TUCUMÁN EN EL TREN 265 DE FERROCENTRAL  1° PARTE
description:
A diferencia de otras veces, la locomotora no es reemplazada en Rosario, por lo que la 9026 cambia sentido de marcha y se pone en el otro extremo del 265.
Una vez instalado en el Pullman Hitachi 520, veo con cierto disgusto como los asientos del coche han sido reemplazados por típicas butacas de omnibús, y además tapizados con bastante mal gusto....
Pasada la 18,00 hs por fin el 265 sale para Tucumán, a esa altura con apenas 300 km recorridos entre Retiro y Rosario, ya acumulaba un atraso de 1 hora y 36 minutos
Saliendo de Rosario Norte, los rayones del blindex adhosado a la ventanilla dificultan bastante la visión, sin embargo, se distinguen la Playa Barrancas, luego el paso a nivel de calle Francia e ingreso a Patio Cadenas, otro paso a nivel de calle Alberdi, Cabin 6 e ingreso a la playa de clasificación de vagones de Patio Parada, dónde la única locomotora identificable es la Gaia 6339 pintada de rojo, cerca del taller Tiro Federal se observa bajo un tinglado el tren gerencial de NCA compuesto por un par de coches Werkspoor pintados de color crema, la grua Takraf 006, algunos viejos coches Birmingham radiados como el SL 985. 
Finalmente en la zona de Ludueña el tren dobla a la derecha y entramos a vía simple.
Hora oficial de salida de Rosario Norte:  16,26 hs.
Hora real de salida de Rosario Norte:     18,02 hs.
Retraso: + 1 hora 36 minutos
Rosario   26-09-2011

CLIP DESCRIPTION:
Fern (Dakota Fanning) convinces her father, Mr. Arable (Kevin Anderson) not to butcher a runt piglet. Instead, she offers to take care of it.

FILM DESCRIPTION:
E.B. White's classic children's story comes to the screen in this live-action adaptation with an all-star voice cast. Fern Arable (Dakota Fanning) is a young girl growing up on her family's farm. When a sow gives birth to some piglets, Fern's father (Kevin Anderson) intends to do away with the runt of litter, but Fern has become attached to the little pig and persuades her father to let him live. The pig, named Wilbur (voice of Dominic Scott Kay), becomes Fern's pet, but when he grows larger, he's put in the care of Homer Zuckerman (Gary Basaraba), a farmer down the road. Fern is still able to visit Wilbur regularly, and it soon occurs to both of them that pigs tend to have a limited life expectancy on a farm, and that unless something unusual happens, Wilbur will eventually becomes someone's dinner. Charlotte, a friendly spider, hatches a plan to make Wilbur seem special enough to save by weaving messages about the "terrific" pig into her web, and she soon persuades her barnyard friends to join in her plan. Charlotte is voiced by Julia Roberts, while the other actors who provide the voices of the animals on Zuckerman's farm include Robert Redford, John Cleese, Oprah Winfrey, Steve Buscemi, Kathy Bates, Cedric the Entertainer. Thomas Haden Church, and André Benjamin.

ANYWAYS!  I have wanted to vid this song with canon Disney for awhile, and when I heard this cover yesterday, I decided it was fate.  So I spent a large portion of my day off today making this video.  Like I said, it's...even more boring than my regular stuff but.  I just wanted to vid.

tags: ['Honda Civic (Automobile Model)', 'oil', 'Smoother', 'CIVIC', 'TYPE-R', 'DYNA PACK', 'Power Check', 'Meeting', "J'S RACING", 'FD2', 'OPTION2', 'JAPAN', 'OSAKA', 'なめらか', '粒子', '体感', 'Power up', '粉', 'POWDER', 'ジェイズレーシング', 'シビック', 'オイルスムーサー', 'オプション２', 'ﾁｭｰﾆﾝｸﾞ', 'TUNING', 'K20A', 'VTEC', 'iVTEC']
description:
Oil Smoother Video-vol.3 CIVIC FD2 at Option2 Power Check Meeting

=Latest Nanoparticle technology　 =

* Significant friction loss reduction due to the nanoparticle diffusion
* Reduction of CO/HC/Nox/CO2
* Higher Combustion Efficiency
* Decrease of noise level


The "Oil Smoother" is a powder type tuning item which is made of 1/17 to 1/20 of the size of oil molecule. When added to the oil molecule, it immediately minimizes the friction between the molecules.

This bearing effect noticeably reduces the friction loss and leads to 1) better throttle response, 2) quieter engine operation, and 3) increase in power & torque.

This product has also been developed as a green product (an environmental product). Based on the governmental smog test and 10.15 Mode test, it is proved that the oil smoother reduces the CO2 by 1 % for every 1km driving.
This product is recommended to any engine and to any driving situation.

Il bianco e dolce cigno cantando more,

Et io moro beato. Morte, che nel morire

Se nel morir altro dolor non sento 
di mille morte il di sarei contento.

title: Toe Scrape And Return Drill - Ice Hockey Power Skating Skate Toe Drag Drill
description:
Full article - http://hockeytutorial.com/skating-tips/how-to-do-the-skate-toe-drag-drill-or-scrape-return-drills/

The Skate Toe Drag Drill or Scrape Return Drills is a fantastic hockey power skating drills for promoting a deep knee bend and long stride and for a low return of the extended foot. This helps skaters that *run* on the ice and kick their feet up to their lower back after each stride. The idea behind the Skate Toe Drag Drill is to use your muscle memory to lock in the proper power skating stride technique.

The Spud, Inc. Magic Carpet Sled is designed to go where traditional metal dragging sleds cannot be used. They can be used inside gyms with rubber or tile flooring, Astroturf, carpet, gym floors, and definitely grass. This sled is more portable than any metal sled, and weighs less than 4 pounds so anyone can carry it. The Magic Carpet Sled is heavy duty and can hold as much weight as a traditional metal sled. This sled has an easy to operate industrial buckle. 


*The Magic Carpet Sled is not to be used on concrete, asphalt or any rough textured surface doing so will damage the sled render it un-useable.

title: [Cover] Always Be With You
description:
HAPPY VALENTINES DAY!!! 

Haha, another English song... my voice sounds weird when I sing in English for some reason. xD

This is such a simple song, yet it's so sweet and beautiful in so many ways. This song is a background song used in Kodocha, an anime which I'm currently watching and in love with. x333 I simply loved this song the first time I heard it! It usually plays in the anime when Sana and Akito have a moment, or when Fuka and Akito have a moment, or Naozumi and Sana have... or simply, when some romantic/sad/sweet moment occurs. xD

Lyrics:
When you're crying I will always be with you
When you're feelin' blue, I will always smile to you

Sadness blows you in to cry
But I won't cry for yesterday
God knows well where you're going to
It's a lonely way...

When you're crying I will always be with you
When you're feelin' blue, I will always smile...

When you're sighing I will always be with you
When you're feelin' blue, I will stand beside you

When you're crying I will always be with you
When you're feelin' blue, I will always smile...

********

I would really like to take this chance to recommend Kodocha to EVERYONE who hasn't seen it. It's seriously a series anyone will enjoy! It's funny, it's dramatic, it's heartwrenching, it's cute, and it's romantic. 

Lol... I just HAD to include Akito's voice in the beginning. I just took it from the episode, opened it in Audacity, and put the echo on. xD It was from the episode where he actually says that he had feelings for Sana. x333 I cried for hours when he finally confessed. Seriously, watch this series...

Please enjoy~!

Song: Always Be With You
Artist: I really... really don't know. ID Maybe Sana's Japanese Seiyuu...
Anime: Kodomo no Omocha (Insert Song)

*I own nothing but my voice*

title: Любительский футбол ЛФЛ СЗАО SFOOT.ru СФутбол 3:2 Центавр-Д
description:
7 ТУР 29.01.2012 СФутбол 3:2 Центавр-Д
Видео и фото матча http://www.Sfoot.ru/SfootCentavrD к сожалению мало видео - очень яркое солнце, снимал со стремянки - эффект отличный смотрится как футбол! надо еще на метр повыше и вообще красота.

Младшая команда школы любительского футбола С.Футбол встретилась в 7 туре с Дублем Центавра зарекомендовавшей себя
в 3-б Дивизионе как один из главных претендентов на повышение. Это активный,дружный и большой коллектив узнаваемый из далека,
со своими традициями,приятно играть с таким организованными клубами, точно знаешь - этим ребятам нужен спортивный успех!
Борьба гарантирована и тем приятнее их обыгрывать) К 7 туру мы закрепились вблизи лидеров с 9 очками и имели шанс выбиться в лидирующую группу,
Центавр-Д по моему должен быть выше своей позиции в Буфере, их настрой и подход к делу намекал на это, и 3 очка с нами позволили бы клубу подтвердить свои амбиции.
Не вовремя наши самые сильные первоклашки школы перешли в старший класс - Таймыр. Но это естественный процесс и сразу 4 футболиста из С.Футбола заиграли в Таймыре -
Олег Терехов, Николай Костырев, Сергей Виноградов и Юрий Литвинов. Помочь нам смог только Николай. В "обновленном" составе против сплоченного Центавра-Д хороший урок.
Игра началась без раскачки, бесполезное солнце слепило но не грело. хотя в первом тайме польза все же была для С.Футбола но как вратарь вытаскивал наши удары я не понимаю?
Принимать мяч было невозможно не то что тащить. Счет открыл Центавр-Д слету точно в ближнюю девятку - красиво жаль ваш вратарь ничего не видел).
Через несколько минут в центральной зоне, Новиков Дмитрий настойчиво выцарапал мяч в сложном подкате, обрезал 6-ых Центавровцев,
и забить оставалось делом техники - а техника у Костырева есть! 1:1. Второй тайм проходил с небольшим преимуществом С.Футбола.
За 10 минут до конца отличился Новиков Д с паса Мартыновченко Т. 2:1. Сесть в оборону напротив жуткого солнца было плохой идеей - Центавр тут же сравнял счет.
В конце после граматнейшего сброса Новиковым Д аута Костырев технично принял мяч и пробил под мышку вратаря, солнце не мешало - Гол!!! 3:2 Очень сложная победа в тяжелейших условиях.
Центавр-Д отличная команда, Спасибо за игру!

title: Crazy: Wild Guitar Player from universe | Bizarre Sirius sound on TV New York | Pleiades performance
description:
English / german - Very bizarre & shrill: Is he an alien from Germany... or a nice guitar player from the Pleiades?
This Les Paul sounds like made on Sirius. Watch those people in the back! Watch the Teflon Fonfara Collages Show!
He performed his Teflon Fonfara Collages Show on TV in the show NEW YORK NIGHTS in 1984.
A historic record!

Teflon Fonfara:
Many years ago, somebody told me: If you perform in New York don't play a regular style. The New Yorkers hate regular guitar performances and they are bored with that. Later, when I came to NY for my first performance in the U.S., I remembered this important info about New Yorkers' taste.
The first gig was a 3-minute long performance on TV in the show "NewYork Nights". It was bizarre & shrill. I scratched my guitar on the floor and this Les Paul sounded like made on Sirius.
This was in 1984!
23 years later I was able to get a hold of this rare video.

Teflon Fonfara:
Vor vielen Jahren sagte jemand zu mir: Wenn Du mal in New York auftrittst, spiele bloß keinen normalen Gitarren-Stil. Das finden die New Yorker langweilig. Als ich später für meinen ersten US-Auftritt nach NY kam, erinnerte ich mich an diesen wichtigen Tipp.
Dieser erste Gig war ein 3-Minuten-Auftritt in der TV-Show "New York Nights". Es war skurril und schrill, ich schrubbte die Les Paul auf dem Boden und sie klang wie vom Sirius.
Dies war im Jahr 1984!
23 Jahre später bekam ich dieses seltene Video.
Schau mal rein...

Home: www.fonfara.de

title: THE RED SLED
Microsoft IllumiRoom Living Room, Interactive Kinect Projection mapping demo
tags: ['Demo', 'Game', 'Demonstration', 'electrictv', 'electrictv.com', 'tv', 'interactive', 'Projection Keyboard (Invention)', 'kinect', 'projection mapping', 'games', 'fun', 'play', 'diablo', 'doom', 'gun', 'gamer', 'Video Game (Industry)', 'Gameplay', 'Room', 'Diablo (Video Game)', 'Bed', 'siggraph', 'siggraph2013', 'movie', 'Entertainment (Word)', 'Tech', '3d', 'hd', 'hdtv', 'research', 'xbox', 'xbox1', '720', '360', 'Illumi', 'room', 'Mano a Mano', 'holodeck', 'roomalive']
description:
"llumiRoom is a proof-of-concept system that augments the area surrounding a television with projected visualizations to enhance traditional gaming experiences. It demonstrates how projected visualizations in the periphery can negate, include, or augment the existing physical environment and complement the content displayed on the television screen. The system can change the appearance of the room, induce apparent motion, extend the field of view, and enable entirely new physical gaming experiences.

The system consists of a projector and a depth sensor that covers a wide area surrounding a television screen. The television provides a traditional, high-resolution gaming experience, and the projector provides low-resolution information for the user's peripheral vision. In contrast to previous work, IllumiRoom does not use flat white projection screens, but instead adapts the projection to the existing viewing environment. The system is entirely self-calibrating and is designed to work in any room.

The demonstration presents 11 example illusions. For instance, it can directly extend the game content into the room by displaying a wide field-of-view rendering of the game on the surrounding physical environment with radiometric compensation. Or it can augment the room to match the theme or mood of the game. For example, the system can can transform the room into a "cartoon world" by super-saturating the colors and adding black silhouette edges. It can also enable physical-virtual gaming experiences by using the 3D data of the room. For example, a grenade can roll out of the television, then bounce off the coffee table, and roll on the floor. All of these effects adapt to the color and geometry of any room.

Brett Jones
University of Illinois, Urbana-Champaign

Hrvoje Benko
Microsoft Research

Eyal Ofek
Microsoft Research"

Andrew Wilson
Microsoft Research

.
@ Siggraph 2013

Se inicia en la noche de la tercera gala de "Reyes del Show" los enfrentamientos de adagio entre las parejas concursantes. La cantante y modelo Leslie Shaw y su soñador Kevin Ubillús entra en disputa con la bella actriz Maricielo Effio y su soñador Elí Vela.

Leslie y Kevin bailan "Algo más" de La Quinta Estación con coreografía de Kervin Valdizán, mientras que Maricielo y Elí hacen lo propio con el tema "Yo no me doy por vencido" de Luis Fonsi, con coreografía de Carlos "El Ché" Suárez.

Emitido originalmente el 19 de noviembre de 2011 en el programa "El Gran Show: Reyes del Show" de América Televisión, conducido por Gisela Valcárcel. Una coproducción de GV Producciones S.A.C. y América Televisión. Video procesado, reestructurado y corregido para YouTube por Nano Cortés-Quiroz.

title: Batman Arkham City Walkthrough Part 37 - Boss - Mr. Freeze
description:
Watch more Batman: Arkham City Walkthroughs videos: http://www.howcast.com/videos/497339-Batman-Arkham-City-Walkthrough-Part-37-Boss-Mr-Freeze

Check out this walkthrough for the open world brawler, Batman: Arkham City, and defeat Mister Freeze.

Victor: Impressive, Batman. I doubted you would actually return.

Batman: I'm a man of my word, Victor. You should know that by now.

Victor: The formula is complete. The bonding process appears to have been successful. How are you feeling? You look unwell.

Batman: Give it to me.

Victor: I'm afraid I cannot do that, Batman. You have given me your last order.

Batman: This is not a time for negotiation.

Victor: I think it is. The clown has my wife. Bring her back to me.

Batman: You don't want to do this, Freeze.

Victor: Oh, I believe I do. You will bring me Nora, or you will die. You are in my world now, Batman.

Batman: Oracle, Freeze is attacking me. Get me the telemetry feed from his suit,now!

Oracle: No problem. Bruce, remember what happened last time. Don't try and take him on in a straight up fight. He's too powerful. Okay, data's ready. Coming through now.

Victor: Hide if you wish, Batman. I will find you and end you. I believed you to be quiet. I was wrong. What? How? So you wish to use magnets against me? I don't think so. There you are. No. Where did you..? That will not happen again. You cannot hide in the cold, Batman. This world is mine. I have you now.

Batman: I can't allow Freeze to see me. He's too dangerous.

Victor: No! I see you are attempting to use my weapons against me. Do you really think I will allow that? No! I can evolve my strat- Get off me! Please, find Nora. She's all I have left. It's over. That was all I could manufacture.

Batman: Harley Quinn took it.

Victor: What are you waiting for? Go and get it back. The clown must pay for what he has done to us.

Batman: It's not that simple. Joker's got the Steel Mill locked down. Getting in will not be easy.

Victor: Perhaps I can help. I've been working on a new projectile system. Maybe these will provide the edge you need.

Batman: I promise you, Victor. I will find Nora.

title: lvl55 HACK everything unlocked Tutorial COD4 1.7 [HD]
description:
Call of Duty 4 makes you unlock weapons, weapon attachments and mods, camouflage, and challenges. Well there is a way around that because all of the data is stored client-side. To unlock all weapons for Call of Duty 4 multiplayer so that you don't have to level up follow these easy instructions.

1. Download this mpdata file.
http://karmarogue.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/11/mpdata

2. Go to Start - Run- Type regedit - Hit Enter.

3. Go to HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE - Software - Activision - Call of Duty 4

4. Double-click codkey

5. Save the key in notepad

6. Replace the key with: DL2J8PY44Q22GE4888D2

7. Press OK and close regedit.

8. Navigate to your Call of Duty 4 profile folder (typically "C:\Program Files\Activision\Call of Duty 4 - Modern Warfare\players\profiles\your_user_name")

9. Back-up and then remove all the files in your user name folder.

10. Place the mpdata file you downloaded in your user name folder

11. Open the COD4 MP game and check your rank. You should now be level 55 with all challenges, guns, and every camouflage unlocked!

12. Finally, in the game go to Options - Multiplayer Options - Key Code and type your original cd key you have saved in notepad.

There you go, you now have everything unlocked. Enjoy.
